and just updated the smart-table.debug.js source. 

To reproduce the issue: Jump to a page greater the 1 in the paginator and press the refresh button. The table jumps back to page 1.

My solution would be following:

Change the stItemsByPage watcher at line 384 to

        scope.$watch('stItemsByPage', function (oldValue, newValue) {
          if (oldvalue !== newvalue) {
            scope.selectPage(1);
          }
        });

